name: 👙 Miami is Too HOTT for Clothes
description:
"👙 Miami is Too HOTT for Clothes #5" by BryantW

When in a Miami bathroom... show off the goods. 

Social Media and Instagram is bringing Depression and a Negative self-image for YOUNG Women and Men to the world one photo at a time. The ideals of beauty normalcy and decency are eroded one "perfect-selfie" at a time. ENJOY A WORLD OF GOONS. 

There is an ugly underside to the "beauty" online.
